{"tid":1169754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中美貿易戰 其實有點似《破壞之王》最後的擂台戰","createTime":"2019-05-24T14:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T11:32:35.000Z","uid":106212,"like":61,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e2d2f1d84353a189a2d919359537384e94415f0b","tid":1169754,"uid":106212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T14:55:01.000Z","msg":"<strong>中國 = 外賣仔 何金銀</strong><br />\n<strong>美國 = 斷水流大師兄</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>第一回合（喬治布殊 年代）：我不動 敵不動</strong><br />\n中國採取「我不動、敵不動」戰術，韜光養悔，秘密發展。見到中國無行動，美國自己都唔敢有大動作。雙方平靜度過第一回合。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>第二回合（奧巴馬 年代）：虛張聲勢</strong><br />\n美國開始想出手 (例如重返亞太、聯日制中)，此時中國開始在場外故弄玄虛，拋鎚仔、拋手榴彈 (即是當時中國崛起初期的發展路線)。<br />\n中國趁機偷襲得手。因為美國都唔知中國實力有幾多，所以第二回合都係無真正開戰。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>第三回合（特朗普 年代）：真正開打</strong><br />\n特朗普認為前任總統和官員都是無能之輩，並向他們說：「在座各位都是垃圾」<br />\n特朗普知道中國無實力，所以決定今個回合正式開戰。開戰後，中國一直處於捱打狀態。<br />\n<br />\n中國目標係 拖到比賽結束 (即是 2020美國總統大選)，到時就會有 奔雷手文泰來 (即是其他的總統候選人 例如拜登) 拯救中國，但都係阻止唔到特朗普。<br />\n四大門派 (華爾街、大企業等等) 都出來阻止特朗普，但特朗普力壓群雄，繼續狙擊中國。<br />\n<br />\n最後，中國決定使出絕招 無敵風火輪 (即是中國製造2025)。但中國需要一個道具 - 幸運輪 (即是高科技產品、晶片等等)。<br />\n<br />\n但係電影和現實嘅不同在於，電影裡外賣仔真係找到幸運輪，但中國唔會得到高科技產品，因為 &hellip;. 都被特朗普禁制咗。<br />\n<br />\n中國可否反敗為勝？大家明啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW 香港都擔當一個好重要角色，就係張學友。以前中國被圍攻到仆街，香港就出手拯救，送畀佢演唱會門票 (即是經濟發展所需嘅資金、技術)。<br />\n<br />\n電影和現實嘅不同在於，電影裡外賣仔會向張學友說：「學友，我愛你」<br />\n但中國就會話：「要不是中央政府照顧你們香港完蛋了」"},{"pid":"7324601c14cbc335c6821d94e574acb1a5f807c3","tid":1169754,"uid":106212,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T14:55:38.000Z","msg":"特朗普向前任總統說<br />\n<img src=\"https://wiki.komica.org/images/8/89/52447.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.komica.org%2Fimages%2F8%2F89%2F52447.jpg&h=6c793414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸人對香港人說<br />\n<img src=\"http://1833.img.pp.sohu.com.cn/images/blog/2008/8/8/2/21/11c44a1532eg213.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1833.img.pp.sohu.com.cn%2Fimages%2Fblog%2F2008%2F8%2F8%2F2%2F21%2F11c44a1532eg213.jpg&h=163129e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人回應<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/7/7d/Shit.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20120302075114\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F7%2F7d%2FShit.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20120302075114&h=222c4875&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70aa0f2957dbca7972715a1f6e8011a993256bea","tid":1169754,"uid":5489,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T14:57:51.000Z","msg":"貨車訓練大法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鎖</span>"},{"pid":"2d5aa56281beb1349b6bd4aabacfb1bef498d197","tid":1169754,"uid":106212,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:12:30.000Z","msg":"食花生睇戲嘅連登仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/24/231138_1ea18af340870f797e90932e634ba2f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F24%2F231138_1ea18af340870f797e90932e634ba2f2.png&h=ff6e3295&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc58526ff389abf279bc395097e21dc3d5c14395","tid":1169754,"uid":106212,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/24/231348_7d7176cb9afd0174f09ebd1f21083f53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F24%2F231348_7d7176cb9afd0174f09ebd1f21083f53.png&h=dccfbeef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1258c7665696633c7a653163f81fcb8c4f7d4bcc","tid":1169754,"uid":246739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a36f746204e8e3c22b1488b2e7bea7606126072","tid":1169754,"uid":106212,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"cit